snippet.title: ZetaZania Part1: Vampire Pirates from Uranus Preview
snippet.description: Whizkin Games presents ZetaZania Part1: Vampire Pirates from Uranus, an upcoming epic 2D side-scrolling platformer computer game, planned for release March 2025.  Filled with unique characters, brilliant storytelling and a British sense of humour, this is a fun, enjoyable and casual game.
